>>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
*> 30AKTEE0 — documents: file access for the AKTE indexed file.
*> Ops: GET by id · FPR by unique file-plan-reference · WRT · ALL
*> (table). L-RET: 00 ok · 23 not found · 22 duplicate · 9x error.
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. "30AKTEE0".
ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
FILE-CONTROL.
    SELECT AKTE-FILE ASSIGN TO "AKTE"
        ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
        ACCESS MODE IS DYNAMIC
        RECORD KEY IS AK-ID
        ALTERNATE RECORD KEY IS AK-FPR
        LOCK MODE IS AUTOMATIC
        FILE STATUS IS WS-FS.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD AKTE-FILE.
COPY "30AKTER0.cpy" REPLACING ==:PFX:== BY ==AK==.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-FS                PIC X(2).
LINKAGE SECTION.
01 L-OP                 PIC X(4).
01 L-RET                PIC X(2).
COPY "30AKTER0.cpy" REPLACING ==:PFX:== BY ==L-AK==.
01 L-AK-TABLE.
   05 L-AK-COUNT        PIC 9(4).
   05 L-AK-ROW OCCURS 300.
      10 L-AK-ROW-ID   PIC X(36).
      10 L-AK-ROW-FPR  PIC X(200).
      10 L-AK-ROW-ORG  PIC X(36).
PROCEDURE DIVISION USING L-OP L-RET L-AK-REC L-AK-TABLE.
MAIN.
    PERFORM OPEN-FILE
    IF L-RET NOT = "00"
        GOBACK
    END-IF
    EVALUATE L-OP
        WHEN "GET " PERFORM DO-GET
        WHEN "FPR " PERFORM DO-BY-FPR
        WHEN "WRT " PERFORM DO-WRITE
        WHEN "ALL " PERFORM DO-ALL
        WHEN OTHER  MOVE "99" TO L-RET
    END-EVALUATE
    CLOSE AKTE-FILE
    GOBACK.

OPEN-FILE.
    MOVE "00" TO L-RET
    OPEN I-O AKTE-FILE
    IF WS-FS = "35"
        OPEN OUTPUT AKTE-FILE
        CLOSE AKTE-FILE
        OPEN I-O AKTE-FILE
    END-IF
    IF WS-FS NOT = "00" AND WS-FS NOT = "05"
        MOVE "91" TO L-RET
    END-IF.

DO-GET.
    MOVE L-AK-ID TO AK-ID
    READ AKTE-FILE
    IF WS-FS = "00" OR WS-FS = "02"
        MOVE AK-REC TO L-AK-REC
        MOVE "00" TO L-RET
    ELSE
        MOVE "23" TO L-RET
    END-IF.

DO-BY-FPR.
    MOVE L-AK-FPR TO AK-FPR
    READ AKTE-FILE KEY IS AK-FPR
    IF WS-FS = "00" OR WS-FS = "02"
        MOVE AK-REC TO L-AK-REC
        MOVE "00" TO L-RET
    ELSE
        MOVE "23" TO L-RET
    END-IF.

DO-WRITE.
    MOVE L-AK-REC TO AK-REC
    WRITE AK-REC
    EVALUATE WS-FS
        WHEN "00" MOVE "00" TO L-RET
        WHEN "02" MOVE "00" TO L-RET
        WHEN "22" MOVE "22" TO L-RET
        WHEN OTHER MOVE "92" TO L-RET
    END-EVALUATE.

DO-ALL.
    MOVE 0 TO L-AK-COUNT
    MOVE LOW-VALUES TO AK-ID
    START AKTE-FILE KEY IS >= AK-ID
    IF WS-FS = "00"
        PERFORM UNTIL L-AK-COUNT >= 300
            READ AKTE-FILE NEXT
            IF WS-FS NOT = "00" AND WS-FS NOT = "02"
                EXIT PERFORM
            END-IF
            ADD 1 TO L-AK-COUNT
            MOVE AK-ID  TO L-AK-ROW-ID (L-AK-COUNT)
            MOVE AK-FPR TO L-AK-ROW-FPR (L-AK-COUNT)
            MOVE AK-ORG TO L-AK-ROW-ORG (L-AK-COUNT)
        END-PERFORM
    END-IF
    MOVE "00" TO L-RET.
END PROGRAM "30AKTEE0".
